data.title: the Road to love
data.meta_description: the Road to love (2019) starring Linda Luca Callejas, Juan Manuel Restrepo, Caterin Escobar and directed by Luis Orjuela.
data.text: This is the story of "La Chiqui", the youngest daughter of a family of truckers. In this universe of trucks, where macho men, popular music, and roadside love stories rule, "La Chiqui" gets pregnant. Her father kicks her out of her family home, forcing her to face a world where no one believes in her because she is a woman. However, she will manage to get ahead with her job, becoming a respected woman in her guild.
